snippet.title: Magical Diary Trailer
snippet.description:
Design your own character to attend a school for magic! Learn spells, make friends, explore dungeons, solve puzzles, and pursue romance.

Game webpage with free demos here:
http://www.hanakogames.com/magical_diary.shtml
